title: About
text:
Cryptocurrencies are very volatile. The data used is from the cryptocurrency market from the top 5 cryptocurrencies. Relevant data from the dataset was sorted and combined to visualize the market spikes. Spikes in individual cryptocurrencies correlate to the crypto market as a whole.
